Package main.java.elsim.models

Class ElevatorShaft

java.lang.Object
main.java.elsim.models.ElevatorShaft
public class ElevatorShaft
extends java.lang.Object
Contains all Information of the elevator shaft. The elevator shaft also contains the elevator car. The elevator car is controlled from the elevator shaft to move it to the individual floors. In addition, this class controls the algorithm with which the elevator car travels to each floor.
Author:
lBlankemeyer

    • nextFloorLeaves

      private Floor nextFloorLeaves()
